sense.def:
Kadar ljudje ali stvari
complement each another
, se dobro ujemajo.

seg.quote: Crisp pastry complements the juicy fruit of an apple pie.
The exercises are an ideal complement to my usual rehearsal methods.

sense.def:
V slovnici je
a complement
eden od sestavnih delov stavčne zgradbe, ki daje podatke o osebku ali predmetu glagola.
